high_descs: Turn towards left and reach the dining table where the knife is placed
Take a knife from the dining table
Turn left and walk straight to reach the table on which microwave oven is placed
Cut a green apple into pieces
Little bit move towards the right side and reach the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the knife inside of the oven and close it
Little bit move towards the left side and reach the side table in which cut apple is placed
Take an apple piece from the cut apple
Little bit move towards the right side and reach the microwave oven again
Open the oven and put the an apple piece inside of the oven and close it. After heating open the oven take back the apple piece and close the oven
Little bit move towards the left side and reach the side table again
Put an apple piece on the side table
anns.task_desc: Put an apple piece on the side table

high_descs: Go to the far side of the circular table just ahead of you.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Go to the larger, rectangular table in the end of this room that has a microwave sitting on it.
Slice the apple on the table.
Go to the microwave on the end of the table.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Look back to the sliced apple.
Pick up one apple slice.
Turn back towards the microwave.
Use the microwave on the apple slice and remove it.
Turn back to the table table.
Put the apple slice down on the left end of the table.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple, microwave one slice and place that slave on a table.

high_descs: Walk nearer to the diningtable.
Take the knife from the top of the round table.
Turn left and walk towards the apple in which oven is placed.
Cut the apple which is on the table.
Move further towards right and reach the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the knife inside the microwave and close the door.
Move a little bit towards the sidetable.
Take a single piece of apple from the cut apple.
Move further towards right and reach the microwave.
Open the door and put the apple in the oven and close the oven. After some minutes, open the door  and take out the apple and close the door again.
Move towards the sidetable.
Put the apple piece on the sidetable below the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple piece on the SideTable just below the fork
